      <txt c="X" a="X" r="X" s="2" w="850" x="40" y="80" delay="0" pt="1" e="-3" align="left">The ship is scheduled to do a canal transit, and all necessary papers are in order. However, the Customs officials are demanding a few cartons of cigarettes from the Captain to let the ship through.

